name: Anarchy Stocking - Panty & Stocking With Garterbelt (Character)
description:
This is a LORA of the character Anarchy Stocking from the anime PSG.

To prompt this character in her angel outfit, enter "<lora:Stocking-PSG:strength>Anarchy Stocking, off shoulder corset dress, white striped thighhighs, hair bow, white choker, sandals,". To prompt this character in her gothic outfit, enter "<lora:Stocking-PSG:strength>Anarchy Stocking, gothic frilled dress, black striped thighhighs, hair bow, mary janes, ". Accessories include "striped sword, mini wings, angel wings, halo, stuffed toy, lollipop,". Prompting "lightshow background," will prompt the transformation sequence background from the show. There's also a few other small outfits trained in here as well.

This LORA looks the best at 0.6 ~ 0.8 strength in my opinion. Stocking was trained on Anythingv4.5 at Clip Skip 2. This lora works great across other models too.
